<p> All of the stuff you just learned was put into a head tag, this will be displayed on the top of your page <br> All of this is now in the body tag, the mid section of your website. Notice the indent.</p>

<strong> <p> Your website starts with a !doctype tag followed by a head, then body, and footer tag.<p> <br> </strong>

